 with clubs divided into a Northern and a Southern section, and teams entering a preliminary group stage. Each section then gradually eliminates the qualifying teams in knock-out fashion until each has a winning finalist. At this point, the two winning finalists faced each other in the combined final for the honour of the trophy.\n\n== Preliminary round ==\n\n=== Northern Section ===\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n{{fb cl header|noqr=y|nopos=y|ptsfirst=y|sort=y|title=Group 1}}\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]\n|'''6'''||2|| 2 ||0 ||0 || 5 || 3 || +3\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Rochdale F.C.|Rochdale]]\n|'''1'''||2 || 0 || 1 || 1 || 2 || 3 || \u22121\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Tranmere Rovers F.C.|Tranmere Rovers]]\n|'''1'''||2 || 0 || 1 || 1 || 1 || 2 || \u22121\n|}\n{{OneLegStart|date=y|team-width=15em}}\n{{OneLegResult|date=Oct 13|Rochdale||0\u20130|Tranmere Rovers}}\n{{OneLegResult|date=Oct 27|Tranmere Rovers||1\u20132|Burnley}}\n{{OneLegResult|date=Nov 24|Burnley||3\u20132|Rochdale}}\n{{end}}\n{{col-2}}\n{{fb cl header|noqr=y|nopos=y|ptsfirst=y|sort=y|title=Group 2}}\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Carlisle United F.C.|Carlisle United]]\n|'''6'''||2 || 2 || 0 || 0 || 3 || 1 || +2\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Chester City F.C.|Chester City]]\n|'''3'''||2 || 1 || 0 || 1 || 3 || 3 || 0\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Blackpool F.C.|Blackpool]]\n|'''0'''||2 || 0 || 0 || 2 || 1 || 3 || -2 \n|}\n{{OneLegStart|date=y|team-width=15em}}\n{{OneLegResult|date=Oct 13|Carlisle United||2\u20131|Chester City}}\n{{OneLegResult|date=Oct 28|Chester City||2\u20131|Blackpool}}\n{{OneLegResult|date=Nov 24|Blackpool||0\u20131|Carlisle United}}\n{{end}}\n{{col-end}}\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n{{fb cl header|noqr=y|nopos=y|ptsfirst=y|sort=y|title=Group 3}}\n|- style=\"background:#ccffcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[Prest